{"tid":2355174,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《棋魂》超越原作，豆瓣評分8.7，榮登2020年度第六神劇","createTime":"2021-01-06T03:24:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T10:32:33.000Z","uid":43785,"like":6,"dislike":279,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"811622a3c6f63a3474175f582b49c07d9378050d","tid":2355174,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:24:20.000Z","msg":"《棋魂》感動超越原作，豆瓣評分8.7，榮登2020年度第六神劇。<br />\n<br />\n《棋魂》豆瓣評分8.7<br />\n《棋魂》被視為2020黑馬劇，改編自許多人心目中的動漫NO.1《棋靈王》。首先，一般漫改劇本來就吃力不討好，因為本身擁有廣大漫迷，如果無法還原大家心目中的角色形象，或是劇情魔改，很容易就被全網黑。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6Tio4zn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6Tio4zn.png&h=052703c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mPRBE7J.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmPRBE7J.png&h=ce74afa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒想到《棋魂》越追越香，大結局後豆瓣評分飆到8.7，劇情節奏好，選角很棒，作為一部漫改劇真的是很難得，中二燃、輕喜劇的調性把控得也很好，這部劇真的是全網吐槽到全網誇，可以一追！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JThtweA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJThtweA.png&h=f56d6fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初頭連登仔狂屌，點知最後評分咁撚高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初個個屌到得6.4，然後劇情好升到8.1，結局依家升到8.7，改得仲感動過原作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全年排第六，竟然屌打好多大製作古裝劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錯過雖然可惜，但你地絕對可以唔睇，<br />\n<br />\n不過呢套，事實上真係冇好似班盲反網友，未睇就鳩UP話佢拍爛左，反而拍得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕對唔似龍珠果D荷里活翻拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0878ea595a61652236b319c879784e0650369d1