://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJThtweA.png&h=f56d6fb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n初頭連登仔狂屌，點知最後評分咁撚高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當初個個屌到得6.4，然後劇情好升到8.1，結局依家升到8.7，改得仲感動過原作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n全年排第六，竟然屌打好多大製作古裝劇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錯過雖然可惜，但你地絕對可以唔睇，<br />\n<br />\n不過呢套，事實上真係冇好似班盲反網友，未睇就鳩UP話佢拍爛左，反而拍得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />絕對唔似龍珠果D荷里活翻拍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:39:46.000Z","msg":"morning sir !"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:28:06.000Z","msg":"早晨"},{"pid":"8810106ab8db5fcc0738fc6f33abcfb13dac0d27","tid":2355174,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f0d7a83104d5533531bfc4ce8b2b753927398f1d","tid":2355174,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:38:04.000Z","msg":"Yes sir"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:28:29.000Z","msg":"NO YES SIR OK？"},{"pid":"fdad62c18d3f6bca057502c19f0e77990121c437","tid":2355174,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"62cc9894d3c42e2ae2875ad80a155b7569cd204b","tid":2355174,"uid":180124,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:23:50.000Z","msg":"豆瓣圍內打飛機都冇10/10<br />\n證明有部分人真係比得好撚低分"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:29:28.000Z","msg":"年度第六，算屌打大卡士架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1dbb2a492a3b4dea0bc656460d7c59c7462ea56","tid":2355174,"uid":180124,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fdad62c18d3f6bca0575